DefaultEvent.Description:
$Aft -> 後部$The onlookers know what is about to happen. They draw closer around her, murmuring. Two of them hold hands.

Then — combustion. The flames catch, so hot and sudden that they vaporize Rosina's ice-water bath in an instant. The bonfire, the smoke, the searing aroma fill the chamber. The ceiling goes black with smoke. 

Afterwards, the bath contains wet ash and a prism of rose-quartz spleen.
DefaultEvent.Name: There's only just time to witness it

ChildBranches.Name: Watch
ChildBranches.Description: Even if you wanted to, you would not be able to leave the chamber quickly enough to avoid seeing what comes next.

Description: Her animescence is at its peak. She can no longer resist.
Name: Rosina's Death
